flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Donor[Donor submits surplus food]
  Donor --> AdminVerify[Admin verifies safety and pickup window]
  AdminVerify -->|Reject| Reject[Notify donor]
  AdminVerify -->|Approve| Req[Approved NGO/orphanage request exists?]
  Req -->|No| Wait[Keep donation approved until request arrives]
  Req -->|Yes| Match[System scores and creates match]
  Match --> Assign[Admin assigns volunteer]
  Assign --> Pickup[Volunteer confirms pickup]
  Pickup --> Deliver[Volunteer delivers food]
  Deliver --> Confirm[Recipient confirms delivery/rating]
  Confirm --> End([End])
